Given this architecture, the siblings dependency relation is modeled by at least one skip-connect. The skip connection will directly feed information forward, and pass gradient backward. The parentto-child relation will be implicitly modeled by skip-connect relation between nodes.

The model recurrently updates the hidden states according to:

mt = h(xt, m0, ..., mt-1, g0t , ..., gtt-1)

